                                                            <h4 class="c-lxyj-title">
                                                                （7）已有基础
                                                            </h4>
                                                            <div class="c-lxyj-content">
                                                                        <div class="c-lxyj-sub">
                                                                            <div class="c-lxyj-sub-title">1.与本项目有关的研究积累和已取得的成绩</div>
                                                                            <div class="c-lxyj-sub-contet">
                                                                                <p style="margin-top:2.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.5pt;&#10;margin-left:36.15pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:125%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;&#10;tab-stops:36.15pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">1.<span style="font:7.0pt " times="" new="" roman""="">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">与本项目有关的研究积累</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%">a.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;&#10;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">掌握</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">C</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">语言高级编程。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%">b.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;&#10;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">了解嵌入式</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">Linux</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">操作系统。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%">c.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;&#10;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">系统掌握电路分析基础、数字电子技术。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%">d.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;&#10;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">参加了学校的电子设计协会，自身对单片机技术的研究与设计具有浓厚的学习兴趣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;&#10;line-height:125%;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p style="margin-top:2.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.5pt;&#10;margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:125%;&#10;tab-stops:39.0pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">2.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:&#10;Calibri">已取得的成绩</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:&#10;125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;tab-stops:39.0pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">a.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">已明确基本的项目实施路线。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%">b.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;&#10;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">现已完成底层程序的编写和基本框架的搭建，开始进行电脑软件模拟以及元器件的选择。</span><br></p>


                                                                            </div>
