                                                                        <div class="c-lxyj-sub">
                                                                            <div class="c-lxyj-sub-title">2.已具备的条件，尚缺少的条件及解决方法</div>
                                                                            <div class="c-lxyj-sub-contet">
                                                                                <p style="text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;&#10;line-height:115%;tab-stops:39.6pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%">1</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">）已具备条件：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;tab-stops:39.6pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">a.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">依托现有的科研实验室提供良好的基础设施资源；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;tab-stops:39.6pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">b.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">已经学完并掌握</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">51</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:&#10;Calibri">单片机基础应用，并在此基础上做了项目，有一定的实践经验。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:&#10;12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;tab-stops:39.0pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">c.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">已有的专业知识的积累和老师的专业指导。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;&#10;margin-left:0cm;mso-para-margin-top:.5gd;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;mso-para-margin-bottom:&#10;.5gd;mso-para-margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;&#10;line-height:125%;layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;&#10;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:&#10;Calibri">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">2</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">）尚缺少的条件：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;tab-stops:39.0pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">a.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">基于单片机的语音识别模块及其算法尚未学习。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;tab-stops:39.0pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">b.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">大数据与云计算技术了解甚微。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

<p style="text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0;&#10;line-height:125%;tab-stops:39.0pt 69.9pt;layout-grid-mode:char"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%">c.Raspberry</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri">微型电脑内部结构以及功能尚未了解。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:125%"></span></p>

